{"tid":1995745,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應林榮基遭潑漆　國台辦：港獨、台獨互勾連","createTime":"2020-04-30T13:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T13:03:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"06793cc5367192451881b6bb84f5e1d977b15e2f","tid":1995745,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Layer200_rm5R8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FLayer200_rm5R8_1200x0.png&h=bda7f345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台北銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基日前在新店開幕前夕，遭潑紅漆，台灣警方隨後逮捕 3 名疑犯。台灣陸委會指對事件高度重視，若查明有中共介入的證據，將以反滲透法治罪。在北京，國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮回應，指鬧劇背後是誰在策劃和政治操弄，相信現在都已經看得很清楚。她又說，港獨及台獨勢力相勾連，目的是搞亂香港，製造麻煩給大陸，必然再令兩岸關係惡化，為台灣社會帶來禍亂。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基本月 25 日，在台北重啟書店前，遭人潑撒紅漆，他之後受訪時表示，認為是有人在警告、恐嚇他。陸委會則指，會調查案件有否危害國家安全的證據。<br />\n<br />\n此前，林榮基亦收到律師信，稱《銅鑼灣書店》的名字已被註冊，禁止他使用。最終林以《中山銅鑼灣書店》為新店名稱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%9E%97%E6%A6%AE%E5%9F%BA%E9%81%AD%E6%BD%91%E6%BC%86-%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%BE%E9%80%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25BD%2591%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258B%25BE%25E9%2580%25A3%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ4OqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=6e91856c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25BD%2591%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258B%25BE%25E9%2580%25A3%2F&h